  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was on a Friday, or Thursday or Friday, and they were distributed throughout the town to people who had, let's say, larger homes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they put in a family or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whatever they could not allocate any rooms, they were actually in the gym and the school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were quartered there, given some sleeping facilities that they should live there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First of all, also, I think that I overlooked one step, that all the Jews had to wear the bands with the David star.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some other areas-- let's say, in our town, was the border, the German borders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the other side of the border, they were wearing yellow David stars with written 'Jude,' which means 'Jews.'",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to wear a band with the-- with the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Radios had-- they were confiscated in the first days, that we should be practically cut off from-- from any news.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The community itself was stricken with various epidemic due to the situation and the hygienic problems.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Therefore, we could not be-- have any possibility to-- to-- People were dying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were decimated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were really without any means of living, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were really very, very poor conditions.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
